"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">J. Rose ed., <i>Feminine Sexuality</i> (1982) p. 56</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">P. Mackay, <i>Kathy Acker and Transnationalism</i> (2009) p. 94</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-14\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-14\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">L. Heywood, <i>Third Wave Agenda</i> (1997) p. 135</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-15\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-15\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">G. C. Spivak, <i>The Post-Colonial Critic</i> (2014) p. 147</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Phallocentrism&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.blackwellreference.com/public/tocnode?id=g9781405183123_chunk_g978140518312339_ss1-2\">Phallus/Phallocentrism</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.litencyc.com/php/stopics.php?rec=true&amp;UID=858\">Phallocentrism</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2238\nCached time: 20180915105051\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.048 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.062 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 389/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 2376/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1064/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 4187/5000